-- Moscow Bourse Council Recommends No Trading on New Year Holidays
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-09-20T13:23:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-20/moscow-bourse-council-recommends-no-trading-on-new-year-holidays.html
The Moscow Exchange’s council
recommended a halt to trading from Dec. 29 through Jan. 7. for
 Russia ’s New Year holidays, according to a statement today on
the bourse’s website.  The council also recommended testing the settlement
clearing system on Jan. 4 and halting the bourse for holidays on
Feb. 23, March 8, May 1 and 9, June 12 and Nov. 4, according to
the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ksenia Galouchko in Moscow at 
 kgalouchko1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  